    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start for the students. But I also want to make sure they understand the different legal perspectives so they don't get confused. Some people argue that focusing too much on 'substantive' due process is a stretch of the Constitution and that we should really just stick to 'procedural' due process. How would you explain that side of the debate to them?",
